Uttar Pradesh
Nov 22, 2014
Murder
Description:
			A man allegedly killed his wife as he suspected her of having an illicit relationship in Kotwali area, police said here today.

Mohammad Ismail strangulated his wife Razia (25) yesterday over illicit relationship in Kanshiram Narag area, SO Ravindra Pratap Singh said.

He said that the accused has been arrested.


